OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew powers proposed to end 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funsafe cladding scandal    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Home developers who refuse to pay the  
OL,6, costs of removing unsafe cladding could
OL,7, have planning permission and projects  
OL,8, blocked under government plans.        
OL,10,FNew powers would also allow cladding   
OL,11,Fcompanies to be sued and subject to    
OL,12,Ffines for defective products.          
OL,14,FThe proposed measures are part of a    
OL,15,FBuilding Safety Bill following the     
OL,16,FGrenfell Tower fire in 2017.           
OL,18,FPeople who are currently facing bills  
OL,19,Fof thousands of pounds to fix their    
OL,20,Fhomes welcomed the move.               
